description:
Take a look at Pergamos from the sky In this Cinematic Aerial Film. It is located approximately  26 kilometres from the modern coastline of the Aegean Sea on a promontory on the north side of the river Caicus and northwest of the modern city of Bergama. When filming for the Lineage 'The 7 Churches of Revelation' series, we captured some incredible views from the skies of Turkey.

🎬 Main Episode: https://youtu.be/udzWshBpEfk
📹 Behind the Scenes: https://youtu.be/0v4b2SP7C5s

Pergamos - the third of the seven Churches of Revelation sits in a beautiful location atop a mountain. This city played a key role in connecting ancient worship with today, and after the message of persecution to Smyrna, this church reveals a condition of compromise. The antidote to compromise is always the straight and pointed truth of Gods Word and many of us need this in our lives to keep us focused on God today.
